    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《跳跳落》</strong>是一款有挑战性的平台跳跃小游戏，玩家操控一名小小刺客，通过移动和跳跃，精确地在平台之间移动。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/071de81a33ef6e0410626991d0a637b9.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=322 /></span><strong>不同的平台</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小小刺客将会遇到不同类型的平台，是时候展现真正的技术了！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/21e50f0c1f1a2df915cfc03dce458d37.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=322 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/403c81a5a459f0b876ef296813ec8cd1.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=322 /></span><strong>皮肤</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游玩来解锁场景和角色的皮肤！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/4a008ea5def4e878e0b575a47ee23e35.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>道具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些平台上会有道具，能帮助你更容易地降落在平台上，通过游玩来升级并强化它们的效果！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/44df93c02f3fb71dc5b88226edab8c87.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>排行榜</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和其他玩家一较高下吧！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/c4352f8bd6bffbd3f2dfbaea1b79f6ea.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p>",
